{"tid":945841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[棋靈王] 28歲青年65歲大媽陷母子戀 擬做試管嬰兒手術","createTime":"2018-12-18T07:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T08:40:59.000Z","uid":35070,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bcf448ad2510086385d1cabdd5bf0cfffde05815","tid":945841,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:41:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/28%E6%AD%B2%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B465%E6%AD%B2%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E9%99%B7%E6%AF%8D%E5%AD%90%E6%88%80-%E6%93%AC%E5%81%9A%E8%A9%A6%E7%AE%A1%E5%AC%B0%E5%85%92%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93-050635638.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F28%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B465%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E9%2599%25B7%25E6%25AF%258D%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2588%2580-%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%2581%259A%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25AC%25B0%25E5%2585%2592%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25A1%2593-050635638.html&d=7SyFeUAMhhGDowNAKCjD9%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=348bcbce\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/28%E6%AD%B2%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B465%E6%AD%B2%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E9%99%B7%E6%AF%8D%E5%AD%90%E6%88%80-%E6%93%AC%E5%81%9A%E8%A9%A6%E7%AE%A1%E5%AC%B0%E5%85%92%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93-050635638.html</a><br />\n<br />\n河南28歲小伙子柱子（化名）去年經歷人生低潮時，遇上65歲芹姓大媽，兩人雖然年紀相差一大截，但在相處中互生好感，柱子被芹婦的溫柔打動，無懼年齡之差談起戀愛。兩人近日更拍了婚紗照，打算朝結婚方向努力。至於兩人擔心的生育問題，芹婦稱如果對方想生孩子，願意考慮做試管嬰兒手術。<br />\n<br />\n柱子在農村出生，每月工資2000元人民幣（約2300港元），曾有一個同齡女朋友。但到了談婚論嫁階段，女方父母索要巨額禮金，令柱子不得不放棄。分手後他又找了一個比自己大10歲的女朋友，惟仍遭女方父母反對。兩段感情失敗都讓他失去信心，甚至出現輕生念頭，這時他遇上了芹婦。<br />\n<br />\n「沒甚麽大不了的，以後還會遇到好姑娘的。」芹婦溫柔地安慰柱子，柱子認為與她相處十分舒服，其後直接向她表白。芹婦笑稱，自己的孫子都17歲了，自己只是比柱子的母親少兩歲，本以為對方只是玩玩，但他一再堅持打動了自己，決定與他嘗試開始。<br />\n<br />\n兩人談戀愛不久便同居，一起逛街、煮飯，沒有別人口中所說的年齡隔閡。雖然偶爾也會吵架，但很快又和好如初。為了減少流言蜚語，柱子還專門把頭髮染成白色，讓芹婦無比窩心。早前柱子決定向芹婦求婚。幸而芹婦的孩子、親人都很支持他們。在雙方親人的祝福下，兩人近日先拍婚紗照，並逐步計劃將來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OP5zmraxI9meHnwHGrBHkA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/6c45283ebcaf5731705dafa4c6e60246\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FOP5zmraxI9meHnwHGrBHkA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F6c45283ebcaf5731705dafa4c6e60246&h=3b60cabf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6adcdc87c4248ae51513826f2ff0fa6c05b97358","tid":945841,"uid":23786,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42075f82235e359a5d342dd9f5309f71b29bc12","tid":945841,"uid":88983,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:43:21.000Z","msg":"鮑姐？"},{"pid":"92470d5a7f6b5ad0daeca7776a56f10ad8575cf5","tid":945841,"uid":59114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> CLS"},{"pid":"ac2b2e3148607d5907eb23dc028c32cfc956c0fd","tid":945841,"uid":179283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:43:37.000Z","msg":"鮑姐"},{"pid":"fc67c3abb1c2771bca8ed162c2fc6244a40a7813","tid":945841,"uid":157197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:44:58.000Z","msg":"識食"},{"pid":"6f70d3fa39e3a91da6fc3559c5ffc9bcc94b7e01","tid":945841,"uid":72688,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:46:17.000Z","msg":"棋靈王真身<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9afa2838756c009257cb7731141cfb814f9049f0","tid":945841,"uid":210851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:46:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc964860b57ab4baf1eb1b3d00b042f